social_posts.post_text:
Me oh my what a year was had!! This is a happy reel, and while there were many happy times, I assure you there were many many hard times…I just don’t feel inspired to photograph those lol😩
2022 was a transformative year for me…and naturally where there is growth there is uncomfort. I I fall in love with my journey more and more because it is uniquely mine and it is making me SO strong. I don’t know what’s ahead, but it does excite me! There is so much more to discover! 🥰Thank you alll for being a part of my journey and for being so supportive! May 2023 continue to bless us with more opportunities, lessons, and laughter!! Big love to u all!❤️‍🔥❤️‍🔥😘

Listen…this one right here hits different, cuz if u know, u KNOW. @beyonce has been my goal since I started my career as a dancer…her standard for excellence and the dedication that she puts into her craft has always inspired me…there is only one and to be in the room with a woman I have admired for years felt surreal but also very assuring that my path has led me to where I am today and I am meant to be right where I am. I am a student of life and I am grateful to continue to be in rooms that allow me to grow and learn..the goal is always to stay hungry to learn🙏🏽

Now, NONE of this would have been possible without the incredible incredible team that is @fatima_noir @iamtiarivera @iamdjdubz 
The experience was truly phenomenal and I’m not just saying that…day in and day out the dancers were appreciated, uplifted, and assured that our gifts were purposeful and meant to be in that space. THANK YOU so much for the opportunity . The team is seriously immaculate .🥹❤️‍🔥

And last but not least, my Drunk in Love ladies 😝😭 I miss y’all already! It was really a pleasure to rock with alll of u on stage. Thank you for making this experience that much better. We did it!! Cheers to many more experiences full of love and growth. 💫💫

Stay motivated and hungry yall! Your dreams are valid and possible! ❤️‍🔥❤️‍🔥❤️‍🔥

#beyonce#dubai#katdiaz#dontstop

Loved this choreo from @denzel_chisolm and @chris1anthony🔥🔥 This is from summer 2021 ✨
I love when I watch videos back and can assess my growth…nothing makes me happier truly 😭 Dance encompasses so much in my life—not only is it fun for me, it literally is my therapy—it makes me feel alive like nothing else, gives me purpose, and everything through it makes so much sense to me. I could cry 🥹 but that’s the Pisces in me haha 
But on a serious note, I make it my mission to constantly be improving because I feel like it’s the least I can do for an art  form that gives and gives to me…so I like to give back to it 🥹🙏🏽 I love u forever and always dance..thank you ❤️‍🔥

Ok ok I’m back from my hiatus 😭 
Had the honor of hitting the stage with @diddy last week at the VMAs as he received his Global Icon award. 
Grateful to the TEAM!! @laurieanngibson @themeagannugent @solundy for everything!! 🫶🏽🫶🏽
To my girlssssss! Thank you for making the experience a good one!! Many laughs were had amongst the madness and craziness  and that I will always be thankful for ❤️

Also the look?! Listennn u know I had to go  out in tHat pony right after cuz the inches were definitely giving a moment lol!💁🏽‍♀️

#VMAs#katdiaz#diddy

My dear Engels. I love u so much. I’ll miss u more than u know. Thank you for being exactly who u were everywhere u went—your smile was contagious and so was that laugh haha. I’ll miss making fun of our Dominican mothers and the words they say that sound made up lol…I’ll miss that cafecito ☕️ moment we always had whenever we linked up…I’ll miss creating with you—my favorite work has been everything we’ve created together. You were always excited to do whatever whenever 🥹. U loved being behind the camera and u were so damn good at it, but I loved watching you dance too—pure joy. I’ll miss watching Wendy with you lol, and compilations of Naomi Campbell walking that runway. I’ll miss hearing you talk about your friends—you were always soo proud and happy of all their accomplishments. I’ll miss you so much Engels. Until we meet again my dear friend. Thank you for your time here and for the influence you had in my life! I love you❤️❤️❤️❤️
#EngelsSantana#oneofone#iloveyou

Ok first voice over so go easy on me 😭! 
Last show tonight in Vancouver 🥹. I love these people SO much! I love this team and I love that we get on that stage and exchange amazing energy each and every time! What a blessing! Thank you @ricky_martin for always leading with love and kindness, you truly are one of one✨🫶🏽. 
You give your heart every night and to watch is beautiful, but to be a part of really feels like a dream 🥹.
To my cast mates, thank you for making every day we’re together never feel like work. You are all beautiful souls and I am so honored to get to share the stage with each and every one of u!!🌟
To the BAND!! Sheesh there is nothing like live music!! Y’all are just amazing!! @tutunpa @congachops @lesterprzz @jotaruizmusic @jacinpaul 
To all the amazing choreographers @luudaddy @catrendic @tracyphillips66 @chonique @lisetteslife thank you so much for everything! This show is so fun to do!🙏🏽🙏🏽❤️

@jillhillier4 and @jlvn1161 THANK YOU for your guidance and for being the absolute best always!!! So much loveeee!!❤️

And with all that being said, so excited for the year ahead!! Thank you all for a beautiful end of the year!! See u so soon!!🫶🏽🫶🏽🫶🏽🫶🏽✨
